{"tid":861569,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【hea唱國歌惹禍】靚女主播被拘留5日","createTime":"2018-10-14T08:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T11:35:26.000Z","uid":193217,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d1ae9d4a1c94896b03aa0dbc72f61906c7c6b245","tid":861569,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T08:43:48.000Z","msg":"(新增內容)內地「虎牙」直播平台人氣靚女主播莉哥（楊凱莉），本月7日晚做直播，用輕佻的態度、手舞足蹈地戲唱國歌，結果引起內地「憤青」不滿，批評她對國歌不敬。上海靜安區警方昨日在微博通報，指莉哥違反了《中華人民共和國國歌法》有關規定，當局依法對她處以行政拘留5日。中共喉舌《人民日報》則在微博發文呼籲「別讓素質趕不上顏值！網絡主播們，該補補課了！」<br />\n據悉，莉哥的直播間已經被封禁，她的相關影像作品亦已全部下架。<br />\n根據《中華人民共和國國歌法》，在公共場合故意篡改國歌歌詞、曲譜，以歪曲、貶損方式奏唱國歌，或者以其他方式侮辱國歌，由公安機關處以警告或者15日以下拘留；構成犯罪的，依法追究刑事責任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4LKONlosqFM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4LKONlosqFM&d=XrEkGR6r2NTAX9QSXkPQ1eargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=5ab21bcb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4LKONlosqFM</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁走音唔識普通話點算"},{"pid":"f763f4a31bd72a3103be16b434a4948bf1597e04","tid":861569,"uid":28765,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T08:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/14/164446_55986886224e40ac83b4fd1321ae737f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F14%2F164446_55986886224e40ac83b4fd1321ae737f.gif&h=f5006b91&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1df3757efbfd98bc652a77ed4075fae3afa41bde","tid":861569,"uid":193217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T08:45:36.000Z","msg":"我覺得已經走火入魔<br />\n咁香港人要拉幾多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3524c8924780b53138ee3ad4584b3adcefd55b62","tid":861569,"uid":104658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T08:47:20.000Z","msg":"起來！我帶你環遊世界"},{"pid":"a7fc72becdf04cb8b803e95620f23adac